item.title: CVE-2024-37063|2024-06-04T12:02:53.320Z -- ydataai -- ydata-profiling
item.description: A cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability in versions 3.7.0 or newer of Ydata's ydata-profiling open-source library allows for payloads to be run when a maliocusly crafted report is viewed in the browser.
